snippet.title: Unleashed - Official trailer
snippet.description:
We are live on Kickstarter! Click this link to support us:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/554713524/unleashed-sins-and-virtues-rpg

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/UnleashedRPG/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/UnleashedRPG
Website: http://unleashed-rpg.com/
Contact: contact@unleashed-rpg.com

Unleashed is a dark RPG themed around sins & virtues.
Explore the world of Mystria as a young adult called Mercy, which has been spared by the curse that unleashed people's primordial sin.

Unleashed has been under development for more than a year. You can follow the game's progress via social medias and via our website.
